 3. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the french##1
 5. the french is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
 6. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 7. the australian is on the left of the japanese##1
 8. the german is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 9. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
10. the japanese is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the french##6
12. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
13. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
14. the person who's sport is cycling is the malaysian##1
15. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
16. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
17. the french is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
18. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
19. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
20. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
