 9. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person eating banana##1
10. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
13. the person who likes yellow is not the person eating cauliflower##6
14. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
15. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
16. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5
18. the person eating pear is not the person who likes brown##6
19. the person eating pear is between the person eating nectarine and the person who likes lilac##2
