 3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
 4. the italian is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
 5. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 6. the french is not the person driving the helicopter##6
 7. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 8. the person driving the train is the polish##1
 9. the italian is not the person driving the motorbike##6
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
11. the spanish is the person driving the van##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
13. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
14. the italian is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the nigerian is not the person driving the train##6
16. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

