 3. the owner of the mouse is not the person eating apricot##6
 4. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 6. the person eating cherry is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
13. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
